’Щ@d008727b34f4427b7a78356e1406d013ea9a966f700c9e628ee8acefafd4babfЩӣTitle: title: roll left
Path: Flags
Content:
``--by, -b {int}``
: Number of columns to roll.
``--cells-only, -c``
: Rotates columns leaving headers fixed.
